\id 2TH  - Ixil, Nebaj NT (ixi) -Guatemala 2010 (DBL -2013) 
\h 2 TESALONICENSES 
\toc1 Ikaꞌv uꞌuj uvaꞌ itzꞌibꞌa bꞌen u Pablo te unqꞌa aa Tesalónica uvaꞌ ni niman u Jesús 
\toc2 2 Tesalonicenses 
\toc3 2 Ts 
\mt1 Ikaꞌv uꞌuj  
\mt2 uvaꞌ itzꞌibꞌa bꞌen u Pablo  
\mt1 te unqꞌa aa Tesalónica  
\mt2 uvaꞌ ni niman u Jesús  
\c 1  
\s1 Ni taqꞌ bꞌen u Pablo itzii  
\p
\v 1 Ineꞌ in Pablo uvaꞌ ni qꞌiilan bꞌen ex, tukꞌ u Silvano tukꞌ u Timoteo. As nuntzꞌibꞌa bꞌen u yoleꞌ sete, ex aa Tesalónica, jankꞌal ex uvaꞌ atoꞌk ex kꞌatz u Kubꞌaal Tiixheꞌ tukꞌ kꞌatz u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo.   
\m
\v 2 As ibꞌaꞌnil kuxh u Kubꞌaal Tiixheꞌ tukꞌ u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo tiꞌ uvaꞌ bꞌaꞌn etatin sevatzaj.   
\p
\v 3 Vitzꞌin vatzik, ni qaqꞌ taꞌntiixh te u Tiixheꞌ setiꞌ, tan aꞌeꞌ bꞌaꞌn te Aak uvaꞌ ech la kubꞌaneꞌ setiꞌ, tan niyakꞌin veꞌt u kꞌujlebꞌal ekꞌuꞌleꞌ as tukꞌ u xoꞌniibꞌeꞌ sexoꞌl.   
\m
\v 4 Estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ ni qoksa veꞌt eqꞌii xoꞌl unqꞌa qitzꞌin qatzikeꞌ uveꞌ ni niman u Tiixheꞌ tu unjoltu unqꞌa tenameꞌ tan kꞌuxh nepalebꞌe kꞌaxkꞌo, as kꞌujleꞌl ekꞌuꞌl tiꞌ Aak. As tul nekuy unqꞌa kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ uvaꞌ nepalebꞌe,   
\m
\v 5 as aꞌeꞌ u kꞌuchbꞌal tetzeꞌ uvaꞌ jik chit kat ibꞌan u Tiixheꞌ tul kat taqꞌ Aak etokebꞌal xoꞌl u tenameꞌ uvaꞌ at jaqꞌ u tijleꞌm u Tiixheꞌ. As tiꞌ uvaꞌ at veꞌt ok ex xoꞌl vitenam Aakeꞌ, as estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ nepalebꞌekat unqꞌa kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ.   
\m
\v 6 As bꞌaꞌn te u Tiixheꞌ uvaꞌ la taqꞌ Aak ichꞌexel te unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ uvaꞌ ni bꞌanon u vaꞌlexheꞌ sete.   
\m
\v 7 As bꞌaꞌn la ibꞌan te Aak uvaꞌ la iꞌl veꞌt oꞌ setukꞌ vatz unqꞌa kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ, oꞌ uvaꞌ kꞌaxbꞌinal veꞌt oꞌ. As aꞌ la ibꞌaneꞌ tul la ilpu veꞌt u tulebꞌal u Kubꞌaal Jesúseꞌ tul uvaꞌ la kuꞌ chꞌuꞌl Aak tu almikaꞌ tukꞌ viyakꞌileꞌ as tukꞌ unqꞌa ángel unpajte.   
\m
\v 8 As la ul Aak tukꞌ mam xamal tiꞌ ul taqꞌat Aak ichꞌexel te unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌ kat niman u Tiixheꞌ. As yeꞌ kat inima kam uvaꞌ ni tal u bꞌaꞌnla yoleꞌ tiꞌ u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo.   
\m
\v 9 As aꞌ uxhchileꞌ uveꞌ la ul u kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ stiꞌ, umaꞌl u kꞌaxkꞌo uvaꞌ yeꞌl iyaꞌtebꞌal. Tan la eesal veꞌt el unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ vatz u Jesús, as yeꞌ la isakꞌ veꞌteꞌ tu uveꞌ ni toksalkat iqꞌii Aak, as yeꞌl tokebꞌal tiꞌ vinimla yakꞌil u Jesús   
\m
\v 10 tu u qꞌiieꞌ uvaꞌ la ulkat Aak. As la oksal iqꞌii Aak tiꞌ u nimla bꞌaꞌnileꞌ uvaꞌ kat ibꞌan Aak sqiꞌ, jankꞌal oꞌ uvaꞌ oꞌ itenam Aak, tan nim talchu Aak. As la chit teqꞌo qaama stiꞌ, oꞌ uvaꞌ oꞌ niman tetz Aak setukꞌ, tan kat enima u bꞌaꞌnla yoleꞌ tiꞌ vibꞌaꞌnil Aakeꞌ uvaꞌ kat qal sete.   
\m
\v 11 Estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ nu kunach Tiixh setiꞌ sbꞌenemeen, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la til Aak u bꞌaꞌneꞌ uvaꞌ nebꞌaneꞌ. As la txuqꞌtxun veꞌt Aak tiꞌ uvaꞌ kat imolo ex Aak. As Aakeꞌ la lochon ex tiꞌ etzojpisat unqꞌa bꞌaꞌnileꞌ uvaꞌ netitzꞌa, tan tiꞌ uvaꞌ kꞌujleꞌl ekꞌuꞌl tiꞌ Aak.   
\m
\v 12 As nu kunach Tiixh setiꞌ, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la oksal veꞌt iqꞌii u Kubꞌaal Jesucristoeꞌ tiꞌ unqꞌa bꞌaꞌneꞌ uveꞌ nebꞌaneꞌ. As la oksal veꞌt eqꞌii taꞌn Aak unpajte tiꞌ u bꞌaꞌnileꞌ uveꞌ kat ibꞌan u Tiixheꞌ sqiꞌ setukꞌ taꞌn u Kubꞌaal Jesucristoeꞌ tan aꞌ vibꞌaꞌnil u Tiixheꞌ kat ibꞌan sqiꞌ setukꞌ.   
\c 2  
\s1 U tulebꞌal u Jesucristo as tukꞌ u tulebꞌal u vibꞌooqꞌol unqꞌa bꞌanol vaꞌlexh  
\p
\v 1 As la val sete, vitzꞌin vatzik, tiꞌ u tulebꞌal u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo as tiꞌ kukꞌulat veꞌt qibꞌ tukꞌ Aak. As la val sete,   
\m
\v 2 tiꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌ la ejalpu etxumbꞌal taꞌn umaꞌtoj chusbꞌal uvaꞌ la alpu sete tiꞌ uvaꞌ kat ilejlu veꞌt u qꞌiieꞌ uvaꞌ alel kan tiꞌ u tulebꞌal u Kubꞌaaleꞌ vatz u txꞌavaꞌeꞌ unpajte. As sotziꞌk ekꞌuꞌl staꞌn. As kꞌuxh la ul tal umaj uxhchil uvaꞌ aꞌ u Tiixhla Espíritu ni alon, as moj in ni alon, as moj in ni tzꞌibꞌan u yoleꞌ sete chaj la taleꞌ,   
\m
\v 3 as etaqꞌak etibꞌ maxtibꞌeloj te u uxhchileꞌ. As vaꞌlexh kuxh veꞌt itxumbꞌal unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ la ibꞌaneꞌ tiꞌ teesal iqꞌii u Tiixheꞌ. As aꞌn la ul ikꞌuch veꞌt tibꞌ u najeꞌ uvaꞌ ibꞌooqꞌol unqꞌa bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ uvaꞌ alel veꞌt kan stiꞌ uvaꞌ la bꞌen tu kꞌaxkꞌo,   
\m
\v 4 tan la ul teesa naj iqꞌii unqꞌa veeꞌ skajayil uvaꞌ tiixh vatz unqꞌa tenameꞌ as tukꞌ unqꞌa veeꞌ ninach unqꞌa tenameꞌ sivaatzil u Tiixheꞌ. As naj la ul toksa veꞌt tibꞌ tiixhil vatz unqꞌa tenameꞌ.   
\m
\v 5 As la etulsa sekꞌuꞌl uvaꞌ kat val kan sete tul uvaꞌ atik in sexoꞌl.   
\m
\v 6 As ootzimaleꞌ setaꞌn abꞌil uveꞌ ni majon ivatz u tulebꞌal vibꞌooqꞌol unqꞌa bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ. Estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ lanal ilej veꞌt iqꞌii as aꞌn la ul veꞌteꞌ,   
\m
\v 7 tan niyakꞌin veꞌt u vaꞌlexhla txumbꞌaleꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌ ootzimalik sqaꞌn sbꞌaxa. Pet lanal eesal el umaꞌl uvaꞌ xoꞌl unqꞌa tenameꞌ u vaaꞌ ni majon ivatz ibꞌooqꞌol unqꞌa bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ.   
\m
\v 8 As aꞌn la ikꞌuch veꞌt tibꞌ u bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ. As aꞌ veꞌt u Kubꞌaaleꞌ la yatzꞌon naj tukꞌ umaꞌl u yol uvaꞌ la tal Aak. As la sotzsal naj taꞌn vilitzꞌkabꞌan Aakeꞌ tul la ul Aak unpajte.   
\m
\v 9 As u bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ tan la ul ikꞌuch tibꞌ naj tukꞌ u tijleꞌm u Satanás. As nim talchu naj la ibꞌaneꞌ, as la ibꞌan naj umaj u kꞌuchbꞌal tetz u tijleꞌmeꞌ uvaꞌ la teqꞌo taama unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ staꞌn. As chulin yol kuxh naj la ibꞌaneꞌ.   
\m
\v 10 As tukꞌ vitxumbꞌaleꞌ uvaꞌ vaꞌlexh kuxhtuꞌ la imaxtibꞌekat unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ uveꞌ la bꞌen tu kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ, tan tiꞌ uvaꞌ kat tixva unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ u jikla yoleꞌ uvaꞌ la qꞌalpun.   
\m
\v 11 Estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ la taqꞌ tzan u Tiixheꞌ umaꞌl u txumbꞌal uvaꞌ xoꞌvebꞌal chittuꞌ tiꞌ unqꞌa tenameꞌ. As la maxtibꞌel unqꞌa tenameꞌ staꞌn, tan aꞌ veꞌt u chuli yoleꞌ la inima unqꞌa tenameꞌ.   
\m
\v 12 Estiꞌeꞌ uvaꞌ ech ibꞌen veꞌt unqꞌa tenameꞌ tu u kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ, jankꞌal uvaꞌ yeꞌ kat niman u jikla yoleꞌ. Pet aal kat chiibꞌ tiꞌ ibꞌanat u vaꞌlexheꞌ.   
\s1 Ni taqꞌ u Pablo taꞌntiixh te u Tiixh tiꞌ uvaꞌ kat itxaa Aak unqꞌa aa Tesalónica tiꞌ isotz ipaav  
\p
\v 13 Pet ech koj oꞌ, vitzꞌin vatzik, tan aal la qaqꞌ taꞌntiixh te u Tiixheꞌ setiꞌ bꞌenameen, ex uvaꞌ xoꞌn ex te u Kubꞌaaleꞌ, tan tiꞌ uvaꞌ kat itxaa ex Aak xeꞌ qꞌiisaj tiꞌ eqꞌalpul vatz vepaaveꞌ tul kat ekꞌujbꞌaꞌ ekꞌuꞌl tiꞌ u jikla yoleꞌ. As tukꞌ u Tiixhla Espíritu kat itxaakat ex Aak   
\m
\v 14 tiꞌ isotzsal epaav tul kat qal u bꞌaꞌnla yoleꞌ sete tiꞌ uvaꞌ la oksal eqꞌii echeꞌ toksal iqꞌii u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo.   
\m
\v 15 Estiꞌeꞌ ni val sete, vitzꞌin vatzik, echabꞌataj ekꞌujbꞌaꞌt ekꞌuꞌl. As yeꞌ la eyaꞌsa enimat unqꞌa chusbꞌaleꞌ uvaꞌ kat kuchus kan sete, as moj unqꞌa yoleꞌ uvaꞌ kat kutzꞌibꞌa bꞌen sete, as enimataj.   
\p
\v 16 Tan xoꞌn chit oꞌ te u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo tukꞌ u Kubꞌaal Tiixheꞌ. As kat toksa Aak u chiibꞌichileꞌ tu u qaanxelaleꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌl iyaꞌtebꞌal. As tiꞌ vibꞌaꞌnil Aakeꞌ ootzimal sqaꞌn uvaꞌ la ibꞌan Aak kam uvaꞌ alel kan sqiꞌ taꞌn Aak.   
\m
\v 17 As Aakeꞌ la yakꞌinsan etaama. As Aakeꞌ la lochon ex tiꞌ ebꞌanat u bꞌaꞌneꞌ as tiꞌ etalataꞌ.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ni tal u Pablo uvaꞌ aꞌ viyol u Tiixheꞌ la oksal iqꞌii  
\p
\v 1 Vitzꞌin vatzik, enachtaj Tiixh sqiꞌ, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la pax veꞌt viyol u Kubꞌaaleꞌ tulaj unqꞌa tenameꞌ. As la oksal veꞌt iqꞌii, echeꞌ uvaꞌ kat ibꞌan sexoꞌl.   
\m
\v 2 As enachtaj Tiixh sqiꞌ, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la eesal el tzan oꞌ vatz unqꞌa bꞌanol vaꞌlexheꞌ tukꞌ unqꞌa bꞌanol txꞌiꞌla aamaileꞌ tan jit chit kajayil unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ uvaꞌ ni niman u chusbꞌaleꞌ uvaꞌ tetz u Tiixheꞌ.   
\m
\v 3 As jik chiteꞌ u Kubꞌaaleꞌ. As Aakeꞌ la yakꞌinsan vetaanxelaleꞌ. As la ikol ex Aak vatz u vaꞌlexheꞌ.   
\m
\v 4 As kꞌujleꞌl kukꞌuꞌl setiꞌ, tan tiꞌ uvaꞌ at veꞌt ok ex kꞌatz u Kubꞌaaleꞌ. As ootzimaleꞌ sqaꞌn uvaꞌ nebꞌaneꞌ kam uveꞌ kat qal sete. As echat kuxh tuk ebꞌaneꞌ tiꞌ ibꞌeneꞌ.   
\m
\v 5 As aꞌ u Kubꞌaaleꞌ la yakꞌinsan vetaanxelaleꞌ, tan tiꞌ uvaꞌ xoꞌn veꞌt ex te u Tiixheꞌ as xoꞌn veꞌt u Tiixheꞌ sete. As la iyakꞌinsa veꞌt Aak vetaanxelaleꞌ, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la ekuy u kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ echeꞌ uvaꞌ kat ibꞌan u Cristo tan kat ikuy Aak u kꞌaxkꞌoeꞌ.   
\s1 Ni tal u Pablo uvaꞌ yeꞌ la iyaꞌsa unqꞌa niman tetz u Jesús ibꞌanat u aqꞌoneꞌ  
\p
\v 6 As tukꞌ vibꞌii u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo tuk qal bꞌen sete uvaꞌ la eteesa etibꞌ kꞌatz unqꞌa qitzꞌin qatzikeꞌ uveꞌ vaꞌlexh kuxh vitxumbꞌaleꞌ. As yeꞌ nibꞌaneꞌ kam uvaꞌ kat kuchus kan sete.   
\p
\v 7 As ootzimaleꞌ setaꞌn uvaꞌ bꞌaꞌneꞌ uvaꞌ ech la ebꞌaneꞌ echeꞌ uvaꞌ nik kubꞌan sexoꞌl, tan yeꞌl oꞌ uvaꞌ vaꞌlexh koj qatineꞌ tukꞌ u kutxumbꞌaleꞌ kat kubꞌan sexoꞌl.   
\m
\v 8 As yeꞌl oꞌ uvaꞌ kat kuxh koj txꞌaꞌn oꞌ tul yeꞌ kat kuchooa. Pet kat aqꞌonvu oꞌ sqꞌiil aqꞌbꞌal tukꞌ koolichil, tan aꞌ nik qaleꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌ la qaqꞌ etaqꞌon tiꞌ etaqꞌat kutxꞌix.   
\m
\v 9 As yeꞌle uvaꞌ yeꞌ koj la uch etaqꞌat qechbꞌubꞌal. Pet aꞌ nik qaleꞌ uvaꞌ la ebꞌan etetz echeꞌ uveꞌ nik kubꞌaneꞌ. As estiꞌeꞌ kat aqꞌonvu oꞌ sexoꞌl.   
\m
\v 10 As tul uvaꞌ atik oꞌ sexoꞌl, as kat kukꞌujbꞌaꞌ kan umaꞌl u yol uvaꞌ ech ni tal ileꞌ: «Asoj at umaj uxhchil uvaꞌ yeꞌ nisaꞌ aqꞌon, as yeꞌl itxꞌix la aqꞌpi.»   
\m
\v 11 As ni qabꞌi yol uvaꞌ at uxhchil sexoꞌl uvaꞌ vaꞌlexh kuxh tatineꞌ tukꞌ vitxumbꞌaleꞌ. As yeꞌ ni taqꞌonveꞌ. Pet nu kuxh toksa tibꞌ xoꞌl unqꞌa uxhchileꞌ tiꞌ unqꞌa yoleꞌ uvaꞌ yeꞌl tetz stiꞌ.   
\m
\v 12 As abꞌil uveꞌ ech nibꞌaneꞌ as tukꞌ vibꞌii u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo ni qalkat bꞌen tiꞌ kubꞌeyat ste uvaꞌ la aqꞌonvi tijikil tiꞌ itxꞌakat ijaꞌmil vitxꞌixeꞌ.   
\m
\v 13 As yeꞌ la yaꞌ ex, vitzꞌin vatzik, tiꞌ ebꞌanat u bꞌaꞌneꞌ.   
\p
\v 14 Pet asoj at umaj uxhchil uvaꞌ yeꞌ la niman uveꞌ ni qal bꞌen tu uꞌujeꞌ, as la etal xoꞌl unqꞌa qitzꞌin qatzikeꞌ. As yeꞌ la uch emolot etibꞌ stukꞌ, aqꞌal uvaꞌ la chꞌixvu veꞌteꞌ tiꞌ uveꞌ nibꞌaneꞌ.   
\m
\v 15 As chꞌoꞌniꞌk etaama stiꞌ, pet la ebꞌeya ste tan titzꞌin etatzik etibꞌ stukꞌ kꞌatz u Kubꞌaaleꞌ.   
\s1 Nitzojpu veꞌt iyolon u Pablo te unqꞌa aa Tesalónica  
\p
\v 16 As aꞌ u Kubꞌaaleꞌ ni bꞌanon uvaꞌ bꞌaꞌn etatin sevatzaj. As Aakeꞌ la aqꞌon sete tiꞌ chit ibꞌeneꞌ. As Aakeꞌ la kaa veꞌt sexoꞌl sekajayil.   
\p
\v 17 As ineꞌ in Pablo nuntzꞌibꞌa bꞌen unqꞌa yoleꞌ sete tukꞌ unqꞌabꞌ tiꞌ unqꞌiilat bꞌen ex. As aꞌ kꞌuchbꞌal tetzeꞌ uvaꞌ in tzꞌibꞌan bꞌen tetz sete, tan ech untzꞌibꞌeꞌ tul nuntzꞌibꞌeꞌ.   
\m
\v 18 As aꞌ vibꞌaꞌnil u Kubꞌaal Jesucristo la kaa veꞌt setiꞌaj sekajayil. An chiteꞌ.   